each load balancer instance distributes evenly across all registered instances in all AZs.

without cross zone:
requests are distributed evenly in individual AZs.

APPLICATION LOAD BALANCER: CZLB always on(can't be disabled). No charges for inter AZ data.
NETWORK LB: disabled by default. You pay for inter AZ if enabled. 
CLASSIC LB:disabled by default. no charges if enabled.


